1. Login AWS Management Console
2. Choose IAM from Servics
3. Click Role
4. Click "Create Role"
5. Choose bellow
	choose "AWS service" from "Trusted entity type"
	Choose "EC2" from "Use case"
	Click "Next"
6. Search and Choose "AmazonSSMFullAccess" from "Permissions policies"
	Click Next
7. Add "SSMFullAccess" to "Role name"
	Click "Create Role"
	
